The core problem is novel:

> A human holds all raw memory, but some subsets are jointly governable by third parties with equal veto, without giving those third parties blanket custody or surveillance.

That combination is not solved by existing IAM, DLP, DRM, ABAC, blockchain consent, or enterprise compliance systems.

